@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy";
}

<h1 class="text-center my-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p class="lead text-center">Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our services.</p>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4">Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p>We may collect the following types of information when you interact with our application:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and other contact details when you register or communicate with us.</li>
                        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about your interaction with the application, such as access times, pages visited, and technical details like IP address and browser type.</li>
                        <li><strong>Library Data:</strong> Details related to books borrowed, returned, or managed within the system.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
                    <p>We use your information for the following purposes:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Providing and managing access to the LibraryManagementAPI application.</li>
                        <li>Enhancing and personalizing user experience.</li>
                        <li>Communicating with you regarding updates, maintenance, or issues.</li>
                        <li>Ensuring data security and compliance with legal obligations.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4">Sharing of Information</h2>
                    <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information. However, we may share your data with:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our application.</li>
                        <li>Complying with legal obligations, government requests, or to protect the rights and safety of our users.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4">Data Security</h2>
                    <p>We take reasonable precautions to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4">Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
                    <p>Our application may use cookies to enhance your browsing experience and track website analytics to improve functionality. You can adjust your browser settings to decline cookies, though this may limit certain features.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4">Your Rights</h2>
                    <p>As a user, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Access your data and receive a copy of it.</li>
                        <li>Correct any inaccuracies in your data.</li>
                        <li>Request the deletion of your data, subject to legal and contractual obligations.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow-sm mb-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h2 class="h4">Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
                    <p><strong>LibraryManagementAPI Support</strong></p>
                    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@librarymanagementapi.com">support@librarymanagementapi.com</a></p>
                    <p>Phone: 03-80524179</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div></p>